PolyForm Noncommercial 1.0.0 — Summary and link

This repository is licensed under the PolyForm Noncommercial 1.0.0 license. For the full, canonical license text, see:
https://polyformproject.org/licenses/noncommercial/1.0.0/

Summary (non-legal, high-level):
- Noncommercial use only: The license permits use, reproduction, modification, and distribution of the Licensed Work only for noncommercial purposes. Commercial use is prohibited without a separate commercial license from the copyright holder.
- Redistribution: If you redistribute the Licensed Work (or derivative works) in source or binary form, you must include the license and copyright notices and comply with the license terms.
- Contributors & modifications: The license governs contributions and derivative works the same way — they remain noncommercial unless a separate commercial license is granted.
- Warranty & liability: The Licensed Work is provided "as is" with no warranties; the license includes typical disclaimers limiting liability.
- Definitions & details: The license defines what counts as "Commercial Use" and other terms; consult the full canonical text for precise definitions and obligations.

Important notes for this project:
- Private development: If you keep the repository private and use it internally, the license is less relevant for public redistribution, but it still documents intended terms if you later publish or share the code.
- If you or your organization wish to use this project commercially, obtain a commercial license from the copyright holder before doing so.

Where to read the full license and get an authoritative copy:
https://polyformproject.org/licenses/noncommercial/1.0.0/

